    title: "Piagam Indonesian Cultural Award ‘94",
    subtitle:
        "Ben mendapatkan piagam penghargaan pada kategori Indonesian Cultural Award ‘94. Ia mendapatkan penghargaan ini  pada acara Indonesian Cultural Award ‘94 dan Penobatan Putri Budaya Indonesia ‘94 yang diselenggarakan oleh Consortium Indonesia Asean Program Consultant. Penghargaan ini ia dapatkan pada tanggal 19 Agustus 1994.\n\nPiagam-piagam ini seolah menjadi pembuktian bagaimana peran Benyamin Suaeb yang pada saat itu aktif menjadi seorang artis dan juga Direktur dari Bens Radio.\n\nBens Radio lahir dari kekhawatiran Ben akan tubuh renta dan otak nya yang mulai menua. Ia pun membuat stasiun radio siaran. Menurut pertimbangannya radio bisa menyelamatkan Ben dari pudarnya popularitas.",
    subtitle2:
        "Ben received an award certificate in the Indonesian Cultural Award '94 category. He received this award at the Indonesian Cultural Award '94 and the Coronation of the Indonesian Cultural Princess '94 which was organized by the Indonesian Asean Program Consultant Consortium. He received this award on August 19, 1994.\n\nThese charters seem to prove the role of Benyamin Suaeb, who at that time was active as an artist and also the Director of Bens Radio.\n\nBens Radio was born from Ben's concern about his aging body and brain. He then created a broadcast radio station. According to his considerations, radio could save him from fading popularity.",
