  Museum(
    title: "FOTO BERSAMA IBU NONI",
    subtitle:
        "Noni Marhaeni lahir 20 April 1940 di Tangerang. Istri pertama Ben ini terbilang kembang Kemayoran dengan kulitnya yang bersih, mata sipit, dan rambut lurus.\n\nNoni mengenal Ben saat ia masih SMA Mereka bertemu lantaran bertetangga. Keluarga Noni mengontrak salah satu rumah yang dimiliki paman Ben. Jaraknya hanya 50 meter dari rumah Ben.\n\nAwalnya Ben merupakan comblang dari Noni dan kawannya, namun kawannya harus ke Banjarmasin sehingga ia memberikan restu kepada Ben untuk memacari Noni. Dari sini Ben mulai mendekati Noni. Mereka pun pernah berpacaran diam-diam.\n\nLika-liku kisah percintaan Ben dan Noni berujung pernikahan pada 2 Oktober 1959. Ben berusia 20 dan Noni 19 tahun. Dari pernikahannya dengan Noni, Ben dikaruniai lima anak.\n\n7 Juli 1979, Ben dan Noni bercerai. Mereka merasa tidak lagi memiliki kecocokan. Pengadilan Agama Jakarta Selatan lah saksi perpisahan mereka diputuskan. Ben dan Noni pun sempat kembali menikah untuk kemudian bercerai kembali.",
    subtitle2:
        "Noni Marhaeni was born April 20 1940 in Tangerang. Ben's first wife was considered the flower of Kemayoran with her clean skin, narrow eyes and straight hair.\n\nNoni met Ben when he was still in high school. They met because they were neighbors. Noni's family rented one of the houses owned by Ben’s Uncle. The distance is only 50 meters from Ben's house.\n\nInitially Ben was a matchmaker for Noni and his friend, but his friend had to go to Banjarmasin so he gave Ben his blessing to date Noni. From here Ben started to approach Noni. Then, they dated secretly.\n\nThe twists and turns of Ben and Noni's love story ended in marriage on October 2 1959. Ben was 20 and Noni was 19 years old. From his marriage to Noni, Ben was blessed with five children.\n\nJuly 7, 1979, Ben and Noni divorced. They feel they no longer have compatibility. The South Jakarta Religious Court was the witness of their separation. After their separation, Ben and Noni once remarried just for redivorced.",
    subtitle3:
        "Noni Marhaeni 于1940年4月20日出生在丹格朗。Ben 的第一任妻子因其洁净的皮肤、细长的眼睛和直发而被誉为 Kemayoran 之花。\n\nNoni 在他还在读高中的时候认识了 Ben。他们相识是因为他们是邻居。Noni 的家人租住了 Ben 叔叔拥有的一栋房子，距离 Ben 的家只有50米。\n\n起初，Ben 是 Noni 和他朋友的媒人，但他的朋友不得不去班贾尔马辛，所以他祝福 Ben 和 Noni 交往。于是，Ben 开始追求 Noni。他们开始秘密约会。\n\n经过几番波折，Ben 和 Noni 的爱情故事最终在1959年10月2日以婚姻告终。当时 Ben 20岁，Noni 19岁。这段婚姻为 Ben 带来了五个孩子的祝福。\n\n1979年7月7日，Ben 和 Noni 离婚了。他们觉得不再有默契。南雅加达宗教法庭见证了他们的分离。在离婚后，Ben 和 Noni 曾复婚，但最终再次离婚。",
    assetImagePath: "assets/data/Karya dan Memori/FOTO BERSAMA IBU NONI.jpg",
    assetAudioPath: "assets/1/ina.mp3",
    assetAudioPath2: "assets/1/english.mp3",
